.title Help: Kernel Debugger
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Kernel Debugger package provides a tool that helps developers port 
and debug kernel modules and device drivers by allowing the developers 
to examine and control a running kernel.

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
